### Additional Formatting Notes
- **No walls of prose.** Maximum 4 consecutive sentences before a visual break (subheading, table, list, or callout box)
- **Bold key terms** on first use throughout — not for emphasis, but to signal defined entities to AI parsers
- **Each H2 section must be self-contained** — a reader (or AI engine) dropping into any section mid-article should be able to understand it without reading what came before
- **Image alt text** (for editorial team): Every image should have descriptive alt text that includes the phrase "studio apartment" plus a qualifier (e.g., "alcove studio apartment floor plan," "studio apartment size comparison chart") — this is a minor but real AEO signal